      <title>科罗拉多州初选的要点：民主社会主义者的又一次胜利</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/01/us/politics/colorado-primary-takeaways.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位民主社会主义者驱逐了丹佛一位资深女议员，一位美国参议员竞选州长失败。但该州的另一位参议员击退了一位进步的初选挑战者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/01/us/politics/colorado-primary-takeaways.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 Jul 2026 13:12:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
